Version 0.7.6 (2026/02/24)
* Fixed an issue where the draw level used in LCA.WorldDrawing can sometimes be
  zero instead of negative
* Added public function: IsInDungeonTrialArena

Version 0.7.5 (2025/11/11)
* Fixed an issue with LCA.MoveableControl that can arise from unexpected
  attempts to stop gamepad movement

Version 0.7.4 (2025/10/14)
* Added flipped variants for a couple of predefined textures for use with
  LCA.WorldDrawing

Version 0.7.3 (2025/09/28)
* Added a number of new predefined textures for use with LCA.WorldDrawing

Version 0.7.2 (2025/09/20)
* Added workaround for LCA.ScreenBorder issues caused by an Update 47 HDR bug
* Minor optimizations for LCA.GroupPanel

Version 0.7.1 (2025/09/13)
* LCA.MoveableControl will now dynamically attach and remove anchor and guide
  lines to slightly reduce memory usage and to remove the template requirement

Version 0.7.0 (2025/09/11)
* Added ToggleGamepadMove function to LCA.MoveableControl, LCA.GroupPanel, and
  LCA.StatusPanel
* Added ToggleAdditionalScene function to LCA.GroupPanel and LCA.StatusPanel
* Added scale option for LCA.GroupPanel and LCA.StatusPanel
* Added a number of new predefined textures for use with LCA.WorldDrawing
* Minor improvements for LCA.WorldDrawing
* Added public function: GetDistanceSquared

Version 0.6.1 (2025/09/03)
* Fixed an issue with texture file paths on console

Version 0.6.0 (2025/09/02)
* Added GetLeftTopPosition function to LCA.MoveableControl, LCA.GroupPanel, and
  LCA.StatusPanel
* Added strikeDead option for LCA.GroupPanel
* Minor bug fixes for LCA.WorldDrawing

Version 0.5.0 (2025/08/25)
* Added SetPositionSnap function to LCA.MoveableControl, LCA.GroupPanel, and
  LCA.StatusPanel
* Added headerHide option for LCA.GroupPanel
* Added public function: GetPlayerUnitId (requires ToggleUnitIdTracking)

Version 0.4.0 (2025/08/23)
* LibCombatAlerts is now available as a standalone download
* LCA.WorldDrawing will now support the optional disableDepthBuffers parameter
* Added public functions: UnpackHSL, UnpackHSLA, MergeTables, and ConcatTables

Version 0.3.0 (2025/08/17)
* Moved LCA's controls out of the global namespace; e.g., LCA_GroupPanel is now
  LCA.GroupPanel
* Added new control: LCA.WorldDrawing
* Added ToggleLock function to LCA.MoveableControl, LCA.GroupPanel, and
  LCA.StatusPanel
* Added headerIcon and headerAlign options for LCA.GroupPanel
* Added public functions: SetTexture, GetTelegraphColor, and UpdateOptions
* Removed the arrow-cw and arrow-ccw textures, which were replaced by the new
  arrow-rotate texture (reverse the texture in-game to change handedness)

Version 0.2.0 (2025/07/23)
* Added console compatibility

Version 0.1.6 (2025/03/07)
* Added public function: CoalescedDelayedCall

Version 0.1.5 (2024/07/05)
* Changed the process of registering l10n strings

Version 0.1.4 (2024/07/01)
* Added public constants: IDS.TAUNT and IDS.MAJ_VULN

Version 0.1.3 (2024/06/16)
* Added public functions: DoesPlayerHaveSingleTargetPullSlotted and
  DoesPlayerHaveTauntOrPullSlotted

Version 0.1.2 (2024/06/10)
* Added public function: GetUnitHealthPercent

Version 0.1.1 (2024/06/09)
* Added inertia to the width of the status panel element if its position is not
  left-anchored, to prevent excessive "jumpy" behavior as the width of its
  content changes

Version 0.1.0 (2024/06/01)
* Initial version
